ration-is-on-her-album-wish-list-3848397">梅根·泰（Megan Thee）的玛格（Megan Thee）公马说，她的“专辑愿望列表”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Megan-Thee-Stallion-and-Doechii.-CREDIT_-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·泰（Megan Thee）种马</a>已经分享说，她很想与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doechii">doechii</a>合作为她的下一张专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-act-ii-review-3806962">梅根·你种马 - &#39;梅根：第二幕评论：休斯顿辣妹2024年结束</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位“野蛮”说唱歌手在最近的Tiktok Live中提出了潜在合作的话题，她在那里对即将发行的专辑“ Megan：Act III”进行了更新。</p><p> “正在制作第三幕，”她现场告诉粉丝。 “我真的只是想弄清楚我想在生活的这一点上做些什么。我只想和那些……一个人，我还没有做一个功能，两个，我是我自己的时间 - 我实际上，你知道，他妈的的人。”</p><p>观众然后开始暗示她与doechii联手，她回答：“我看到doechii，bit子，我爱doechii。”</p><p>她补充说：“我确实想和doechii一起做一首歌。” “那是在我的列表上。那是在我的专辑愿望清单上。”</p><p>梅根（Megan）继续确认她“现在没有歌曲”，这对于Doechii出现是有意义的，并补充说：“我觉得Doechii将是您必须在录音室中与歌曲合作的人。</p><p> “我想听听她想说唱的节拍，而且我也想挑战自己说唱自己通常不会失去自己的节拍。” </p><figure id="attachment_3833969" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833969" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833969" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty.jpg" alt="doechii" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Doechii-2025-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833969" class="wp-caption-text"> Doechii在第67届格莱美奖的红地毯上。学分：录音学院的凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>“第三幕”将跟随2024年的“梅根：第二幕”，该书收到了<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-act-ii-review-3806962">发光五星级评论</a>，读：“关于&#39;Act II&#39;，Megan确认了她为什么再次成为“现在最糟糕的bit子”。</p><p> “尽管近年来困扰着她的所有逆境，但她还是像说唱公主一样坚定地站在说唱世界上，从基座上凝视着她的山顶 - 也许很快就会出现加冕典礼。”</p><p> LP还进入了<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">2024年列表中的50张最佳专辑</a>，而曲目“ Hiss”在我们<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596">2024年的50首最佳歌曲</a>中赢得了第10位。</p><p>同时，Doechii今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-drops-new-song-nosebleeds-in-celebration-of-grammy-win-3833956">在格莱美奖上获得了最佳说唱专辑奖</a>，成为仅次于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauryn-hill">Lauryn Hill</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi b的</a>第三位女性冠军。为了庆祝胜利， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doechii-drops-new-song-nosebleeds-in-celebration-of-grammy-win-3833956">她发行了“流鼻血”</a> ，在其中说唱着表现出反对者。</p><p> Doechii的“ Nissan Altima”被列为<i>NME</i> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596#23">2024年50首最佳歌曲</a>之一。 <i>NME</i>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/doechii-alligator-bites-never-heal-review-3788938">“ Aligator Bites永不治愈”的四星级评论</a>中分享道：“ Doechii在此版本中陷入了痛苦的态度，但是 - 最后 - 她找到了慰藉和力量，使混音带更像是她情感旅程的声音日记。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-says-a-doechii-collaboration-is-on-her-album-wish-list-3848397">梅根·泰（Megan Thee）的玛格（Megan Thee）公马说，她的“专辑愿望列表”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
